Notes
 This map does not come with a nav file. I will either include this in an update or next release, or not include it at all.
General Info
 Readme:
make of the classic aim_sniperYard, this version is source-ified,and winter-ized. Some familiar players may recognize some original features, Such as the idle truck. You may also note some new features, such as new hallways and a new staircase. Either way, enjoy the map. If you have any problems, contact me, and I'll see to getting an update to fix any problems one may encounter. GWSOD CS Studios: fpsbanana.com/studios/1335 GWSOD CS Homepage: geocities.com/peteswebworld/CS/Homepage.html -GeeZee
Known Issues
I have already recieved reports of the map crashing servers. I have not confirmed this. I do know that this map does not crash while playing offline. I can not identify the problem at this time.
